Install ZeroServices and its dependencies (pip install -r requirements.txt in zeroservices root).
Launch api_realtime.py, power.py and worker.py.
Run bower install to install JS dependencies.
Launch "python -m SimpleHTTPServer".
Access the Web UI on "http://localhost:8000".
Play with the API on "http://localhost:5001/power/" and see the result on the Web UI.
Have fun!
